entry.content:
Music Name : Antares Citizen - 1st Hyperspace Launch

Author : Antares Citizen
SoundCloud

Author Words "The view from the ground was a stunning sight.

The sky was a brilliant tapestry of light and color, a gentle breeze rustled through the air, carrying with it the faint hum of the hyper speed launch from Earth.

At the center of it all was the launch pad, ready to launch its payload into the depths of space at hyper speed. Bright blue and orange flames illuminated the launch pad, with a deep rumble that echoed throughout the city.

As the launch began to ascend, the horizon lit up with a vibrant beam that radiated outwards the cityscape in a beautiful display of cosmic energy. The launch quickly disappeared into the night sky, leaving behind a stunning view of the distant euphoric future that laid before us, a beautiful sight to behold.

Farewell Kosla. "
